   <p>For GWs dealings with that particular party of Cherokee, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-05-02-0014&amp;expandNote=GEWN-02-05-02-0014-fn-0004#GEWN-02-05-02-0014-fn-0004" class="document">GW to Dinwiddie, 24 Oct. 1757, n.4</a>.</p>

</div>
